---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ButtonLink from '../components/ui/ButtonLink.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Join / Collaborate" description="Find ways to work with DRAGGON Lab.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Join / Collaborate</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">DRAGGON Lab is based at the University of Bristol in the School of Engineering Mathematics and Technology. We welcome expressions of interest from students, postdocs, collaborators, open-source contributors, and partners.</p>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-slate-600">When you contact the lab, include who you are, what stage you are at, what part of DRAGGON Lab interests you, and whether you are looking for a project, collaboration, contribution, partnership, or initial conversation.</p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3"><ButtonLink href="mailto:contact@draggonlab.org">Email DRAGGON Lab</ButtonLink><ButtonLink href="/project-directions" variant="secondary">Explore Project Directions</ButtonLink></div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
